  <brief_title>Pregabalin (Lyrica) for the Treatment of Essential Tremor</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-site, Double-blind, Randomized, Placebo-controlled, Crossover Study of Pregabalin (Lyrica, PGB) in the Treatment of Essential Tremor</official_title>
