  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This will be a multi-site, prospective, double-blind, randomized, placebo-controlled,
      crossover trial conducted over 6 months to assess the effectiveness and safety of PGB to
      treat symptoms of ET.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
